wt179\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> to <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/work\" title=\"work\">work</a>, to <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/function\" title=\"function\">function</a>","parsedExamples":[{"example":"Die Uhr <b>tut</b>’s nicht mehr.","translation":"The clock doesn’t <b>work</b> anymore."}],"examples":["Die Uhr <b>tut</b>’s nicht mehr."]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt182\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> to <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/make_a_difference\" title=\"make a difference\">make a difference</a>; to be different","parsedExamples":[{"example":"<b>Tut</b> sich das viel<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">?</span>","translation":"Does that <b>make</b> much of <b>a difference</b>?"},{"example":"Die beiden Kameras <b>tun</b> sich nichts.","translation":"The two cameras <b>are</b> no <b>different</b> [i.e. neither better than the other]."}],"examples":["<b>Tut</b> sich das viel<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">?</span>","Die beiden Kameras <b>tun</b> sich nichts."]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt186\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> to <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/happen\" title=\"happen\">happen</a>, to be <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/go_on\" title=\"go on\">going on</a>","parsedExamples":[{"example":"Und, <b>tut</b> sich heute etwas<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">?</span>","translation":"Well, anything <b>happening</b> today?"},{"example":"Derzeit <b>tut</b> sich viel.","translation":"There's a lot <b>going on</b> at the moment."}],"examples":["Und, <b>tut</b> sich heute etwas<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">?</span>","Derzeit <b>tut</b> sich viel."]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt190\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span>  <span class=\"use-with-mention\" about=\"#mwt191\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">Used with the <u>preceding</u> infinitive of another verb that has been fronted to the first position, typically for strong emphasis or contrast with another verb</span>","parsedExamples":[{"example":"Er singt immer noch gern, aber tanzen <b>tut</b> er gar nicht mehr.","translation":"He still loves singing, but as to dancing, he doesn't <b>do that</b> anymore at all."}],"examples":["Er singt immer noch gern, aber tanzen <b>tut</b> er gar nicht mehr."]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt193\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> <span class=\"use-with-mention\" about=\"#mwt194\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">Used with the <u>following</u> infinitive of another verb, without fronting, to convey continuousness or general emphasis on an action</span>","parsedExamples":[{"example":"Ich <b>tu</b> doch zuhören<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span>","translation":"I <i><b>am</b></i> listening! (as a response to the reproach that one is not)"},{"example":"Ich <b>tu</b> das jetzt mal aufräumen.","translation":"I<b>’m</b> cleaning this up now."}],"examples":["Ich <b>tu</b> doch zuhören<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span>","Ich <b>tu</b> das jetzt mal aufräumen."]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt197\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> <span class=\"use-with-mention\" about=\"#mwt198\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">Used in the past subjunctive with the infinitive of another verb to form the conditional tense (instead of standard <i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"de\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/würde#German\" title=\"würde\">würde</a></i>)</span>","parsedExamples":[{"example":"Ich <b>tät</b> mir das noch mal überlegen.","translation":"I <b>would</b> reconsider that."}],"examples":["Ich <b>tät</b> mir das noch mal überlegen."]}]}],"ha":[{"partOfSpeech":"Preposition","language":"Hausa","definitions":[{"definition":"<a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/since\" title=\"since\">since</a>, <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/ever_since\" title=\"ever since\">ever since</a>"}]}],"jv":[{"partOfSpeech":"Noun","language":"Javanese","definitions":[{"definition":"<a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\